title: Sawbones: Patient Privacy
description:
This week, Dr. Sydnee's dad Tommy Smirl sits in for Justin as they explore the history of patient privacy. Why does the doctor have to keep your secrets? Find out this week!

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
